_vrf_PLAT971_CU-525
;
PROBLEM: Check Calcd Resid. Dens.  1.06Ang From Zn2             2.68 eA-3  
RESPONSE: This alert arises from unresolved electron density located near the Zn 
center, at a distance of approximately 1 Å. This couldn't be any unassigned atom. 
Despite considerable efforts to improve the data quality, we were unable to obtain 
a higher-quality dataset .
;
_vrf_PLAT973_CU-525
;
PROBLEM: Check Calcd Positive Resid. Density on       Hf1       1.73 eA-3  
RESPONSE:  Residual electron density is found near heavy atoms due to the poorly diffracting crystal.
;
# end Validation Reply Form




